title: Life of a War Emperor After Retirement – Manhuaus
alternative_titles: Wu Wi Yinju Zhihou de Shenguo
The Martial Emperor's Life After Seclusion
summary: Life of a War Emperor After Retirement Manhua Ever since he transversed into the realm, he turned into an adorable, lovely, androgynous man, who is coveted by many. Fortunately, Ling Ge has a mysterious physique and his strength automatically grows. After touring around Eastern China and finally suppressing the western gods in a single battle, he has been called the Martial Emperor since then. Subsequently, the androgynous martial emperor has been living in seclusion. Nonetheless, he became friends with a young loli, and the androgynous Martial Emperor came out of seclusion again!
